        <div class="panel panel--50-50 panel--contained   panel--50-50--right-image">
            <div class="panel__inner">
                <div class="panel__image-block" style="background-image: url(https://bcu.imgix.net/conservatoire-event-133083970482815678.jpg?auto=format&amp;fm=jpg);"></div>
                <div class="panel__text-block">

                    <h2 class="panel__heading">Royal Birmingham Conservatoire Open Day</h2>

                        <div class="panel__text"><p><span>Join us on Thursday 6 June for our Royal Birmingham Conservatoire Open Day to get </span><span>a real insight into life as a conservatoire student. T</span><span>ake</span><span> part in introductory talks, tour our £57 million music building and meet our trailblazing academics and inspiring students.</span></p></div>

